Motorist are advised to use alternative routes as the R56 was closed this morning due to protest action. Road Traffic Inspectorate spokesperson, Zinhle Mali, said they were informed the protest action has to do with Eskom related issues. “The community members are there striking over electrical issues and have blocked off the road. “We have informed the relevant role-players and for now the road is closed and motorists are advised to use other routes,” said Mali.